hadiths[161]{hadithnumber,text}:
3801,"Muhammad-bin-Yahya bin hibban ne Aaraj se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mulaamisa aur munaabiza ki khareed-bikri se mana farmaya."
3802,"abu-Zinad ne Aaraj se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se isi ki tarah riwayat ki."
3803,Hafs bin Aasim ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se isi ki tarah riwayat ki.
3804,Abu-Saleh ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se usi ki tarah riwayat ki.
3805,"Amr-bin-Dinar ne Ata-bin Mina se riwayat ki ke unhon-ne un ( ata ( ko Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se hadis bayan kartey huey suna, unhon-ne kaha : 2 qism ki khareed-bikri (yani ( mulaamisa aur munaabiza se mana kya gaya hai. mulaamisa ye hai ke donon ( bechney waley aur kharidney waale) mein se har aik baghair sochey (aur ghaur kiye ( apne sathi ke kapdey ko chhuey, aur munaabiza ye hai ke donon mein se har aik apna kapda doosrey ki taraf phainkey aur kisi ne bhi apne sathi ke kapdey ko) jiske sath iske kapdey ka tabadla ho raha hai) na dekha ho. (aur usi se saude ki takmeel ho jaey. ("
3806,"Yunus ne mujhey ibne-Shahab se khabar di, unhon-ne kaha : mujhey Aamir bin Sad-bin-abi-Waqas ne bataya ke Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hamein 2 qism ki khareed-bikri aur 2 qism ke pahnawon se mana farmaya : saude mein aap ne mulaamisa aur munaabiza se mana farmaya, mulaamisa ye hai ke koi aadmi doosrey ke kapdey ko din mein ya raat mein apne hath se chhuey aur uske ilawa usey ulat kar bhi na dekhey aur munaabiza ye hai ke koi aadmi doosrey aadmi ki taraf apna kapda phainkey aur doosra uski taraf apna kapda phainkey aur baghair dekhey aur) baghair haqiqi ( razamandi ke yahi unki Sauda ho."
3807,Saleh ne ibne-Shahab se isi sanad ke sath yahi hadis bayan ki.
3808,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kankar phenk kar Sauda karne aur dhokey wali Sauda se mana farmaya hai."
3809,"Leis ne Naafe se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abdullah (bin umr (Raziallahu anhu)) se aur unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki ke aap ne hablul-habla ke saudey se mana farmaya hai."
3810,"Ubaidullah se riwayat hai, unhon-ne kaha : mujhey Naafe ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se khabar di, unhon-ne kaha : ahal jahiliyat oont ke gosht ki hablul-habla tak Sauda kartey they. aur hablul-habla ye hai ke ontni ( maada) bachcha janey , phir wo bachcha jo paida hua hai, haamla ho (uski ya uske gosht ke saudey) to Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhein us se mana farma diya."
3811,"Imam Malik ne Naafe se, unhon-ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : tum mein se koi kisi ke saudey par Sauda na kare."
3812,"Ubaidullah ne kaha : mujhey Naafe ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se khabar di, unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki ke aap ne farmaya : koi aadmi apne ( musalman ( bhai ke saudey par Sauda na karey aur na apne ( musalman ( bhai ke paigham nikah par paigham bhejey , siwaey-iske ke wo usey ijazat de."
3813,"Ismail bin Jafar ne hamein Alaa se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne apne walid ( Abdur-Rehman ( se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : koi musalman kisi musalman ke saudey par saude bazi na kare."
3814,"Ahmed bin Ibrahim Dorqi ne mujhey yahi hadis bayan ki, kaha : mujhey Abdus-Samad ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein Shoba ne Alaa aur Suhel se hadis bayan ki, un donon ne apne apney walid ( Abdur-Rehman bin Yaqoob aur Abu-Saleh samaan ( se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki, neez hamein Muhammad-bin-Musanna ne yahi hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein Abdus-Samad ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein Shoba ne Aamash se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Abu-Saleh se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se, unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki, neez Ubaidullah-bin-Muaz ne hamein hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein mere walid ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein Shoba ne Adii-bin Sabit se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne abu-Hazim se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us se mana farmaya ke koi aadmi apne ( musalman ( bhai ke kiye gaey saudey par Sauda karey, aur Dorqi ki riwayat mein) (saum akheeh) ki bajaey) ( chhotey se saudey (ke alfaz hain."
3815,"Aaraj ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : saude ke liye qafley ke sath rastey mein (ja kar) mulaqat na ki jaey, na tum mein se koi doosrey ke saudey par Sauda karey, na kharidney ki niyat ke baghair mahz bhaaw badhaney ke liye qeemat lagaao, na koi shehri kisi dehati ke liye Sauda karey aur na tum ontni aur bakri ka doodh roko, jisne unhein iske baad khareed liya to unka doodh dohney ke baad usey 2 baton ka ikhtiyar hai : agar usey wo pasand hai to usey rakh ley aur agar usey na-pasand hai to aik saa khajoor ke sath usey wapas kar de."
3816,"Muaz Anbari ne kaha : hamein Shoba ne Adi-bin Sabit se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne abu-Hazim se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ( tijarati ( qaaflon ko aagey ja kar (unke raston mein) milney se, shehri ko kisi dehati ke liye Sauda karne se, aurat ko apni ( musalman ( behan ki talaaq ka mutalba karne se, mahz bhaw chadhaney ke liye qeemat lagaaney se, janwar ke thanon mein doodh rokney se, aur apne bhai ke kiye gaey saudey par Sauda karne se mana farmaya,"
3817,"ghandar, Wahab bin Jarir aur Abdus-Samad bin Abdul-Waris sab ne kaha : hamein Shoba ne isi sanad ke sath Shoba se riwayat ki hui Muaz ki hadis ki tarah hadis bayan ki, ghandar aur Wahab ki hadis main ( majhool ke seedhey ke saath) hai : mana kya gaya hai aur Abdus-Samad ki hadis mein) Maruf ke seedhey ke saath) hai : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mana farmaya,"
3818,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ( kharidney ke iraadey ke baghair ( bhaw chadhaaney ke liye qeemat lagaaney se mana farmaya,"
3819,"ibne-abi-Zayda , Yahya-bin-Saeed aur) Abdullah ( ibne-Numair , un sab ne Ubaidullah se, unhon-ne Naafe se, unhon-ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mana farmaya ke bazar mein pahunchne se pahley saman hasil kya jaey. ye ibne-Numair ke alfaz hain aur doosrey donon ne kaha : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ( samane-tijarat laney walon ko) rastey mein ja kar milney se mana farmaya,"
3820,"Imam Malik ne Naafe se, unhon-ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se Ubaidullah se ibne-Numair ki riwayat ki hui hadis ki tarah riwayat ki."
3821,Hazrat Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ( rastey mein) ja kar saman tijarat leney se mana farmaya.
3822,"Hushaim ne hamein Hisham se khabar di, unhon-ne Ibne-Sirin se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ( rastey mein) ja kar bahar se laey janey waley saman tijarat ko hasil karne se mana farmaya,"
3823,"ibne-Juraij ne kaha : mujhey Hisham Qurdosi ne Ibne-Sirin se khabar di, unhon-ne kaha : maine Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, wo keh rahe they, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : saman tijarat ko rastey mein ja kar hasil na karo. jisne bahar mil kar unse saman khareed liya, to jab uska Malik bazar mein aayega to usey ( Sauda ko bar-qaraar rakhney ya fasakh karne ka ( ikhtiyar hoga."
3824,"abu-Bakar-bin-abi-Sheba , Amr Naqid aur Zuber bin Harab ne kaha : hamein Sufiyan ne Zohri se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Saeed-bin-Musaiyab se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, wo us ( sanad) ko Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tak pahunchaatey they, aap ne farmaya : koi shehri kisi dehati ke liye Sauda na kare. Zuhair ne kaha : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat hai ke aap ne is baat se mana farmaya ke koi shehri kisi dehati ki taraf se Sauda kare."
3825,"Taaus ke betey ne apne walid se, unhon-ne Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne is baat se mana farmaya ke bahar nikal kar qafley walon se mila jaey aur us se ke koi shehri kisi dehati ki taraf se Sauda kare. (Taaus ne) kaha : maine Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se puchha : aap ke farman : koi shehri dehati ki taraf se (sauda na karey) ka kya mafhoom hai? unhon-ne jawab diya : wo uska dalaal na baney."
3826,"Yahya-bin-Yahya tamimi aur Ahmed bin Yunus ne kaha : hamein abu-Khaseema Zuhair ne hadis sunai, kaha : hamein abu-Zubair ne Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : koi shehri kisi dehati ki taraf se Sauda na kare. logon ko chhod do, Allah Taala unmein se kuchh ko kuchh ke zariey se rizq deta hai. albatta Yahya ki riwayat main ( majhool ke seeghey ke saath (passive voice)) hai : rizq diya jata hai."
3827,"Sufiyan-bin-Uena ne hamein abu-Zuhair se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se, unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se usi ki tarah riwayat ki."
3828,"Yunus ne Ibne-Sirin se, unhon-ne Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : hamein mana kya gaya hai ke koi shehri kisi dehati ki taraf se Sauda karey, chahe wo iska bhai ho ya walid ."
3829,"Ibne-Aun ne hamein Muhammad (bin Sirin ( se hadis bayan ki, kaha : Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : hamein is baat se mana kya gaya ke koi shehri kisi dehati ke liye Sauda kare."
3830,"Musa bin Yasar ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jisne doodh roki gaee bhed (ya bakri ( khareed li to wo usey lekar ghar wapas aaey aur uska doodh nikaley, agar wo uske doodh deney se razi ho to usey rakh ley , warna khajoor ke aik saa samet usey wapas kar de."
3831,"Suhel ke walid ( Abu-Saleh ( ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jisne aisi bhed (ya bakri ( khareed li jiska doodh roka gaya hai to usey teen din tak iske barey mein ikhtiyar hai, agar chahey to rakh ley aur chahey to wapas kar de aur uske sath khajoor ka aik saa bhi wapas kare."
3832,"Qurra ne hamein Muhammad (bin Sirin ( se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jisne doodh roki hui bhed (ya bakri ( khareed li to usey teen din tak ikhtiyar hai. agar wo usey wapas karey to iske sath ghalley ka aik saa bhi wapas karey, gandam ka nahi."
3833,"Sufiyan ne hamein Ayub se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Muhammad (bin Sirin ( se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jisne doodh roki hui bakri khareed li, usey 2 baton ka ikhtiyar hai. agar chahey to usey rakh ley aur agar chahey to usey wapas kar de, aur khajoor ka aik saa bhi wapas kar de, gandam ka nahi."
3834,"abdul-wahaab ne Ayub se isi sanad ke sath hadis bayan ki, lekin unhon-ne kaha : jisne ( doodh roki hui ( koi bhed ya bakri khareedi usey ikhtiyar hai."
3835,"Hammam-bin-Munabba se riwayat hai, unhon-ne kaha : ye hadisein hain jo hamein Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se bayan kin, iske baad unhon-ne kai hadisein bayan kin, unmein se aik ye thi : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jab tum mein se koi doodh roki gaee ontni ya bhed (ya bakri ( khareed ley to usey iska doodh nikalney ke baad 2 baton ka ikhtiyar hai ya to wo ( janwar ( le-ley warna khajoor ke aik saa samet usey wapas kar de."
3836,"Hammad ne hamein Amr-bin-Dinar se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Taaus se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jisne ghalla khareeda to wo usey pura kar leney se pahley aagey farokht na kare. Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : main har cheez ko usi ki tarah khayal karta hun."
3837,Sufiyan-bin-Uena aur Sufiyan Sory ne Amr-bin-Dinar se isi sanad ke sath usi ke mutabiq riwayat ki.
3838,"Mamar ne ibne- Taaus se khabar di, unhon-ne apne walid se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jisne ghalla khareeda to wo usey farokht na karey yahan tak ke usey apne qabzey mein ley ley. Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : main har cheez ko ghalley ki tarah samajhta hun."
3839,"abu-Bakar-bin-abi-Sheba , abu-Kuraib aur Ishaq-bin-Ibrahim ne hamein hadis bayan ki. padhi. Ishaq ne kaha : hamein khabar di aur doosrey ne kaha : hamein hadis bayan ki. padhi. Wakee ne Sufiyan se, unhon-ne ibne- Taaus se, unhon-ne apne walid se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jo ghalla khareedey to usey aagey farokht na karey yahan tak ke usey maap (kar qabzey mein ley) ley. (Taaus ne kaha :) maine Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se puchha : kyon ? unhon-ne jawab diya : kya tum dekhtey nahi ke log soney ke iwaz ( ghalla ( khareedtey hain halanke ghalla muakhkhar hota hai. abu-Kuraib ne apni hadis mein, , muakhkhar hota hai, nahi kaha,"
3840,"Abdullaah-bin-Muslima Qanabi ne hamein hadis sunai, kaha : hamein Malik ne hadis sunai aur Yahya-bin-Yahya ne hamein hadis sunai, kaha : maine Malik ke samney qirat ki ke Naafe se riwayat hai, unhon-ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jo shakhs ghalla khareedey to pura hasil karne se pahley usey farokht na kare."
3841,"Yahya-bin-Yahya ne pichhli sanad ke sath Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke zamaney mein ham ghalla khareeda kartey they, to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ham par aisey aadmi muqarrar farmatey jo hamein hukm detey ke usey farokht karne se pahley us jagah se jahan ham ne usey khareedaa tha, kisi dusri jagah muntaqil karein."
3842,"Ubaidullah ne Naafe se, unhon-ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jo shakhs ghalla khareedey to wo usey pura kar leney tak aagey farokht na kare."
3843,"neez unhon (hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu)) ne kaha : ham ahale-qaafila se baghair maap (aur wazan) ke ghalla khareedaa kartey they, to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hamein mana farmaya ke ham usey , uski jagah se muntaqil karne se pahley, aagey farokht karein."
3844,"Umar-bin Muhammad ne Naafe se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jo shakhs ghalla khareedey to usey pura kar leney aur apne qabzey mein leney se pahley farokht na kare."
3845,"Abdullah-bin-Dinar se riwayat hai ke unhon-ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jo shakhs ghalla khareedey to usey qabzey mein leney se pahley aagey farokht na kare."
3846,"Mamar ne Zohri se, unhon-ne Salim se, unhon-ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke zamaney mein agar wo ( wazan aur maap ke baghair ( andaazey se ( dher ki sura mein) ghalla khareedtey aur usko muntaqil karne se pahley usi jagah farokht kartey to is par unko mar padti thi."
3847,"Yunus ne mujhey ibne-Shahab (Zohri ( se khabar di, unhon-ne kaha : mujhey Salim bin-Abdullah ne bataya ke unke walid ( Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu)) ne kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke zamaney mein logon ko dekha ke jab wo ( naap-tol ke baghair ( andaazey se ghalla khareedtey to is baat par unhein mar padi thi ke wo usko gharon mein muntaqil karne se pahley , usi jagah usey bechein. ibne-Shahab ne kaha : mujhey Ubaidullah bin-Abdullah-bin-Umar ne hadis bayan ki ke unke walid andaazey se ghalla khareedtey , phir usey apne ghar utha laatey."
3848,"abu-Bakar-bin-abi-Sheba, ibne-Numair aur abu-Kuraib ne kaha : hamein Zaid-bin-Hubab ne Suhak bin Usman se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Bukair bin-Abdullah-bin ashajj se, unhon-ne Sulaiman-bin-Yasar se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jo shakhs ghalla khareedey to usey naap kar leney se pahley aagey farokht na kare. Abu-Bakar ki riwayat main ( من الشترى ( ki bajaey) 'manittaba' (pairvi) ke alfaz hain ( mana aik jaisey hain. ("
3849,"Abdullah-bin-Haaris makhzumi ne hamein khabar di, kaha : hamein Suhak bin Usman ne Bukair bin-Abdullah-bin ashajj se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Sulaiman-bin-Yasar se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke unhon-ne Marwan se kaha : tum ne soodii tijarat halal kar di hai? Marwan ne jawab diya : maine aisa kya kya hai? Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : tum ne adaaeygi ki dastaawez (chekon) ke saudey halal qarar di hai halanke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mukammal qabza karne se pahley ghalley ko bechney se mana farmaya hai. kaha : is par Marwan ne logon ko khutba diya aur un (chekon) ke saudey se mana kar diya. Sulaiman ne kaha : maine muhaafizon ko dekha wo unhein logon ke hathon se wapas ley rahe they."
3850,Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) farmaya kartey they : jab tum ghalla khareedo to usey poori tarah qabzey mein leney se pahley na becho.
3851,"ibne- Wahab ne hamein hadis bayan ki, kaha : mujhey ibne-Juraij ne hadis bayan ki ke abu-Zubair ne unhein khabar di, unhon-ne kaha : maine Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, wo ke rahe they : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne khajoor ki us dheri ko, jiska maap malum nahi, khajooron ke muaiyan maap ke iwaz bechney se mana farmaya hai."
3852,"Rooh bin Ubada ne hamein hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein ibne-Juraij ne abu-Zubair se khabar di, unhon-ne Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, wo keh rahe they : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mana farmaya, padhi. usi ( uper zikr ki gaee riwayat ( ki tarah, lekin unhon-ne hadis ke aakhir mein) من التمر (ke alfaz zikr nahi kiye."
3853,"Imam Malik ne Naafe se aur unhon-ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Sauda karne waley donon mein se har aik ko apne sathi ke khilaf (sauda faskh karne ka ( ikhtiyar hai jab tak wo juda na hon, siwaey-iske ke ikhtiyar wali Sauda ho."
3854,"Ubaidullah, Ayub, Yahya-bin-Saeed aur Suhak ne Naafe se, unhon-ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se, Naafe se Imam Malik ki hadis ki tarah riwayat ki."
3855,"Leis ne hamein Naafe se khabar di, unhon-ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki ke aap ne farmaya : jab 2 aadmi aapas mein Sauda karein to donon mein se har aik ko) saudaa khatm karne ka ( ikhtiyar hai jab tak wo donon juda na ho jayen aur ikatthey hon. ya un donon mein se aik doosrey ko ikhtiyar de, agar unmein se aik doosrey ko ikhtiyar de aur usi par donon Sauda kar lein to Sauda lazim ho gaya, aur agar aapas mein Sauda karne ke baad donon juda huey aur unmein se kisi ne Sauda ko tark nahi kya to bhi Sauda lazim ho gaya."
3856,"Zuhair-bin-Harab aur ibne-abi-Umar donon ne Sufiyan se riwayat ki. Zuhair ne kaha : hamein Sufiyan-bin-Uena ne ibne-Juraij se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : mujhey Naafe ne (hadis) imla karaai ke unhon-ne Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, wo keh rahe they : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jab 2 Sauda karne waley aapas mein khareed w farokht karein to unmein se har aik ko apne saude ( ko khatm karne) ka ikhtiyar hai jab tak wo aapas mein juda na hon ya unka Sauda ikhtiyar se hua ho ( unhon-ne ikhtiyar istemal kar liya ho. ( agar unka Sauda ikhtiyar se hua hai to lazim ho gaya hai. ibne-abi-Umar ne apni riwayat mein izafa kya ke Naafe ne kaha : jab wo ( ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu)) kisi aadmi se Sauda kartey aur chahtey ke wo aadmi unse saude ki waapsi ka mutalba ( اقالہ ( na karey to wo (khiyaar majlis khatm karne ke liye) uthtey, thoda sa chaltey, phir uske paas wapas aa jatey."
3857,"Abdullah-bin-Dinar se riwayat hai ke unhon-ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se suna wo keh rahe they. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : 2 Sauda karne walon ke darmyan (is waqt tak) Sauda ( lazim ( nahi hota, yahan tak ke wo aik doosrey se juda ho jayen, siwaey-iske ke khiyaar ( ikhtiyar ( wala Sauda ho. (jis mein khiyaar ki muddat tay kar li jaey ya ikhtiyar istemal karke Sauda ko pakka kar liya jaey.)"
3858,"abu-Khaleel ne Abdullah-bin-Haaris se, unhon-ne Hazrat Hakeem-bin-Hizaam (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki, aap ne farmaya : Sauda karne waley donon fareeqon ko ikhtiyar hai jab tak juda na hon. agar wo donon sach bolein aur haqiqat ko waazeh karein to unke saude mein barkat dali jati hai, aur agar wo jhoot bolein aur (aib wghaira) chipaaein to unke saude se barkat mitaa di jati hai."
3859,"Abu-Tayyah se riwayat hai, unhon-ne kaha : maine Abdullah-bin-Haaris se suna, wo Hakeem-bin-Hizaam (Raziallahu anhu) se hadis bayan kar rahe they, unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se usi ki tarah riwayat ki. imam Muslim-bin Hajjaj (Rehmatullahi-alaih) ne kaha : Hazrat Hakeem-bin-Hizaam (Raziallahu anhu) Kaba ke andar paida huey they aur unhon-ne 120 saal zindagi paai."
3860,"Ismail bin Jafar ne Abdullah-bin-Dinar se riwayat ki, unhon-ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, wo keh rahe they : aik aadmi ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se kaha ke usey saude mein dhoka de diya jata hai. to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : tum jis se bhi Sauda karo to keh diya karo : dhoka nahi hoga. ( iskey baad) wo jab bhi Sauda karta to kehta : dhoka nahi hoga."
3861,"Sufiyan aur Shoba donon ne Abdullah-bin-Dinar se isi sanad ke sath usi ki tarah hadis bayan ki, lekin un donon ki hadis mein ye alfaz nahi hain : wo jab saudaa karta to kehta tha : dhokaa nahi hoga."
3862,"Imam Malik ne Naafe se, unhon-ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne (is waqt tak darakhton par lagey huey) phalon ke saudey se mana farmaya yahan tak ke unki ( pakney ki) salahiyatein zahir ho jaey. aap ne bechney waley aur kharidney waley donon ko) aisi Sauda se) mana farmaya,"
3863,"Ubaidullah ne hamein Naafe se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se, unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se usi ki tarah riwayat ki."
3864,Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne khajoor ke saudey se mana farmaya yahan tak ke wo surkh ya zard ho jaey aur khel ( satte) (ke saude) se yahan tak ke wo ( daney bhar kar) safaid aur aafaat se mehfooz ho jaey. aap ne bechney aur kharidney waley donon ko mana farmaya.
3865,"Jarir ne hamein Yahya-bin-Saeed se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Naafe se, unhon-ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : tum phal mat khareedo yahan tak ke unki salahiyatein zahir ho jaey aur us se aafat (ka imkan) khatm ho jaey. ( ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne) kaha : uski salahiyatein (zahir honey) se uski surkhi aur zardi murad hai."
3866,"abdul-Wahab ne Yahya se isi sanad ke sath yahan tak ke uski salahiyatein waazeh ho jaey tak hadis bayan ki, iske baad wala hissey bayan nahi kya."
3867,"ibne-abi Fudaik ne hamein hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein Suhak ne Naafe se khabar di, unhon-ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se, unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se abdul-wahaab ki hadis ki tarah riwayat ki."
3868,"Musa-bin-Aqba ne mujhey Naafe se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se, unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se Imam Malik aur Ubaidullah ki hadis ki tarah riwayat bayan ki."
3869,"Ismail bin Jafar ne Abdullah-bin-Dinar se riwayat ki ke unhon-ne ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : tum phal na becho yahan tak ke uski salahiyatein zahir ho jaey."
3870,"Sufiyan aur Shoba donon ne Abdullah-bin-Dinar se isi sanad ke sath hadis bayan ki, Shoba ki hadis mein ye izafa hai ke ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se kaha gaya : uski salahiyatein se kya murad hai? unhon-ne kaha is se aafat ( borgar janey aur bimari lag janey (ka waqt khatm ho jaey."
3871,"abu-Zubair ne hamein Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne (is waqt tak) darakht par lagey phal ko bechney se mana farmaya, padhi. ya kaha : hamein mana farmaya, padhi. yahan tak ke wo theek ho jaey."
3872,Amr-bin-Dinar ne hadis bayan ki ke unhon-ne Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se suna wo keh rahe they : Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne (is waqt tak) darakht par lagey phal ko bechney se mana farmaya yahan tak ke uski salahiyatein zahir ho jaey.
3873,"abu bakhtri se riwayat hai, unhon-ne kaha : maine Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se khajoor ke saudey ke barey mein malum kya to unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne khajoor ke saudey se mana farmaya yahan tak ke wo us se khud kha sakey ya wo khaaey janey ke qaabil ho jaey, aur yahan tak ke iska wazan kya ja sakey. maine kaha : iska wazan kiye janey se kya murad hai? unke paas maujood aik shakhs ne kaha is (ke wazan (ka andaza lagaya ja sakey."
3874,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : ( darakhton par laga hua) phal na khareedo yahan tak ke uski salahiyatein zahir ho jaey."
3875,"hamein Yahya-bin-Yahya ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein Sufiyan-bin-Uena ne Zohri se khabar di, neez hamein ibne-Numair aur Zuhair-bin-Harab ne hadis bayan ki. padhi. alfaz unhi donon ke hain. padhi. donon ne kaha : hamein Sufiyan ne hadis bayan ki ke hamein Zohri ne Salim se, unhon-ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se, unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki ke aap ne ( pakney ki) salahiyatein zahir honey se pahley phal ke saudey se aur phal ko khushk khajoor ke iwaz bechney se mana farmaya."
3876,ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : hamein Zaid-bin-Saabit (Raziallahu anhu) ne hadis bayan ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Sauda araayaa ki ijazat di. ibne-Numair ne apni riwayat mein ye izafa kiya : ( ijazat di (ke usey bechaa (ya khareedaa ( jaey.
3877,"ibne-Shahab se riwayat hai, unhon-ne kaha : mujhey Saeed-bin-Musaiyab aur abu-Salma-bin-Abdur-Rehman ne hadis bayan ki ke Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : phal ( pakney ( ki salahiyatein zahir honey se pahley mat khareedo aur na khushk khajoor ke iwaz ( darakht par laga ( phal khareedo. ibne-Shahab ne kaha : mujhey Saalim-bin-Abdullah-bin-Amr ne apne walid se hadis bayan ki. unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki, bilkul usi ki tarah."
3878,"ibne-Shahab ne Saeed-bin-Musaiyab se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Muzaabna aur Muhaaqla ke saudey se mana farmaya, Muzaabna ye hai ke khajoor par lagey phal ko khushk khajoor ke iwaz farokht kiya jaey. aur Muhaaqla ye hai ke kheti ko) katney se pahley) gandam ke iwaz farokht kiya jaey. aur zamin ko gandam ke iwaz kiraaey par diya jaey. (ibne-Shahab ne) kaha : mujhey Saalim-bin-Abdullah ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se khabar di ke aap ne farmaya : salahiyatein zahir honey se pahley phal na khareedo , aur na (darakht par lagey) phal ko khushk khajoor ke iwaz khareedo . Salim ne kaha : mujhey Hazrat Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ne Hazrat Zaid-bin-Saabit (Raziallahu anhu) se khabar di, unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki ke aap ne us ( manaahi ke aam hukm (ke baad ariya ke saudey mein taro-taazaa ya khushk khajoor ke iwaz saudey ki rukhsat (chhut) di, aur uske siwa kisi saudey mein rukhsat nahi di."
3879,"Imam Malik ne Naafe se, unhon-ne ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se, unhon-ne Hazrat Zaid-bin-Saabit (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ariya waley ko ijazat di ke wo usey (is par maujood phal ko) miqdar ka andaza kartey huey khushk khajoor ke iwaz baich ley."
3880,"Sulaiman-bin-Bilal ne hamein Yahya-bin-Saeed se khabar di kaha : mujhey Naafe ne khabar di ke unhon-ne Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, wo hadis bayan kar rahe they ke Hazrat Zaid-bin-Saabit (Raziallahu anhu) ne unhein hadis bayan ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ariya ke barey mein rukhsat (chhut) di ( ariya ye hai) ke ghar waley (apni taraf se diye gaey darakht ke phal ka ( khushk khajoor ke hawale se andaza laga kar usey ley lein taake wo taaza khajoor kha sakein."
3881,abdul-wahaab ne hamein kaha ke maine Yahya-bin-Saeed se suna wo keh rahe they : mujhey Naafe ne isi sanad se usi ki tarah khabar di.
3882,"Hushaim ne hamein Yahya-bin-Saeed se isi sanad ke sath khabar di, albatta unhon-ne kaha : ariya se wo khajoor ka darakht murad hai jo logon ko) bataur Atiya ( diya jata hai. wo ( darakht par lagey phal ko) andaazey ke baqadr khushk khajooron ke iwaz farokht kar detey hain."
3883,"Leis ne hamein Yahya-bin-Saeed se khabar di, unhon-ne Naafe se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : mujhey Zaid-bin-Saabit (Raziallahu anhu) ne hadis bayan ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ariya ko (is se hasil honey wali) khushk khajoor ki miqdar ke andaazey se farokht karne ki ijazat di. Yahya ne kaha : ariya ye hai ke koi aadmi apne ghar walon ki khuraak ke liye khajoor ka taaza phal (is se hasil honey wali) khushk khajoor ke andaazey ke iwaz khareed ley. (ye tareef taaza phal leney waley ke nuqta nazar se hai. mafhoom aik hi hai.)"
3884,"Abdullah-bin-Numair ne hamein hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein Ubaidullah ne hadis sunai, unhon-ne kaha : mujhey Naafe ne ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Hazrat Zaid-bin-Saabit (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne araayaa mein rukhsat di ke us (ke phal (ka andaza kartey huey usey khajoor ki maapi hui miqdar ke iwaz farokht kar diya jaey."
3885,"Yahya-bin-Saeed ne Ubaidullah se isi sanad ke sath hadis riwayat ki, aur) farokht kar diya jaey ki bajaey) hasil kar liya jaey ke alfaz bayan kiye."
3886,Ayub ne Naafe se isi sanad ke sath riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne araayaa ke saudey mein iske andaazey ki miqdar (ke hisab se lein-dein ( ki ijazat di.
3887,"Sulaiman-bin Bilal ne hamein Yahya-bin-Saeed se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne bushair bin Yasar se, unhon-ne apne gharaaney se talluq rakhney waley Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke kuchh sahaba se, jin mein Sehal bin abi Hasma (Raziallahu anhu) bhi shamil hain, riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ( darakht par lagey ( phal ko khushk khajoor ke iwaz farokht karne se mana farmaya aur aap ne farmaya : ye sood hai, yahi ( Sauda ( Muzaabna ( khajoor ke darakht par lagey huey phal ko khushk khajoor ke iwaz farokht karna ( hai. haan , albatta aap ne ariya ko bechney ya kharidney ki ijazat di ( ghariya ye hai) ke koi khandan aik 2 khajoor ke darakht (jo bataur Atiya de gaey ( unse hasil honey wali khushk khajoor ke andaazey ke mutabiq ley lein taake wo iska taaza phal khaaein (aur jinhein darakht diye gaey hain, unhein khushk khajoor de dein. ("
3888,"Leis ne hamein Yahya-bin-Saeed se khabar di, unhon-ne Bushair bin Yasar se aur unhon-ne Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke) kuchh ( sahaba se riwayat ki ke unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ariya ko (is se hasil honey wali) khushk khajoor ki miqdar ke andaazey se farokht karne ki ijazat di."
3889,"Muhammad-bin-Musanna , Ishaq-bin-Ibrahim aur ibne-abi-Umar sab ne ( abdul-wahaab ( Saqafi se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine Yahya-bin-Saeed se suna wo keh rahe they : mujhey Basheer-bin-Yasar ne apne khandan se talluq rakhney waley Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke kuchh ashaab se khabar di ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mana farmaya, aagey Yahya se Sulaiman-bin Bilal ki hadis ( 3887 ( ki tarah hadis zikr ki. lekin Ishaq aur ibne- Musanna ne lafz rabba ki bajaey lafz (zaban) (Muzaabna) istemal kya hai, phir bhi ibne-abi-Umar ne ribaa hi kaha."
3890,"Sufiyan-bin-Uena ne hamein Yahya-bin-Saeed se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Basheer-bin-Yasaar se, unhon-ne Sehal bin abi Hasma (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki. unhi ( Sulaiman, Leis aur Saqafi) ki hadis ke ham mana."
3891,"Waleed bin Kasir ne kaha : mujhey banu-Haarisa ke Maula Basheer-bin-Yasaar ne hadis bayan ki ke Rafe-bin-Khadeej aur Sehal bin abi Hasma (Raziallahu anhu) donon ne usey hadis bayan ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Muzaabna , yani taaza khajoor ki khushk khajoor ke iwaz Sauda se mana farmaya, siwaey araya walon ke kyonke unhein Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ijazat di thi."
3892,"Yahya-bin-Yahya ne kaha : maine Imam Malik se puchha : kya aapko Daawood-bin-Husain ne ibne-abi Ahmed ke aazad karda ghulam Abu-Sufiyan ( Wahab ( se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se hadis bayan ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne araayaa ko panch wasq se kam ya panch wasq tak andaazey se bechney ki rukhsat di hai? . padhi. (Imam Muslim (Rehmatullahi-alaih) Mina ne kaha : ( shak Dawud ko hai ke unhon ( Abu-Sufiyan ( ne panch wasq kaha ya panch wasq se kam kaha, padhi. to unhon (Imam Malik ( ne jawab diya : haan."
3893,"Imam Malik ne Naafe se, unhon-ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Muzaabna se mana farmaya aur Muzaabna se murad ( khajoor ke taaza ( phal ko khushk khajoor ki maapi (ya toli hui) miqdar ke iwaz aur angoor ko munaqqa ki maapi (ya toli hui) miqdar ke iwaz farokht karna hai."
3894,"Muhammad-bin-Bishr ne kaha : hamein Ubaidullah ne Naafe se hadis bayan ki ke Hazrat Abdullah (bin umr (Raziallahu anhu)) ne unhein khabar di ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Muzaabna se mana farmaya, aur Muzaabna ye hai ke khajoor ke taaza phal ko khushk khajoor ki maapi hui miqdar ke iwaz becha jaey aur angoor ko munaqqa ki maapi hui miqdar ke iwaz becha jaey aur) khoshon mein) gandam ki kheti ko maapi hui miqdar ke iwaz bechaa jaey."
3895,ibne-abi-Zayda ne Ubaidullah se isi sanad ke sath usi ki tarah riwayat ki.
3896,"abu-Usama ne ham se bayan kya, kaha : hamein Ubaidullah ne Naafe se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Muzaabna se mana farmaya aur Muzaabna ye hai ke khajoor ke (taaza) phal ko khushk khajoor ke maap ki muqarrara miqdar ke badley aur angoor ko munaqqa ke maap ki muqarrara miqdar ke badley farokht kya jaey aur kisi bhi phal ko andaazey ki buniyad par (usi tarah) farokht karne se mana farmaya."
3897,"Ismail bin Ibrahim ne hamein Ayub se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Naafe se, unhon-ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Muzaabna se mana farmaya aur Muzaabna ye hai ke khajoor par jo phal laga hua hai usey maap ki muqarrara miqdar ke sath khushk khajoor ke iwaz becha jaey ke agar badh gaya to mera aur agar kam ho gaya to uski zimme-dari bhi mujh par hogi."
3898,Hammad ne Ayub se isi sanad ke sath usi ke ham-mana hadis bayan ki.
3899,"Qutaiba-bin-Saeed aur Muhammad-bin Rumeh ne Leis se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Naafe se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Muzaabna se mana farmaya (Muzaabna ye hai) ke koi aadmi apne baagh ka phal agar khajoor ho to khushk khajoor ke muqarrara maap ke iwaz farokht karey aur agar angoor ho to munaqqa ke muqarrara maap ke iwaz farokht karey aur agar kheti ho to ghalley ke muqarrara maap ke iwaz usey farokht kare. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne un sab (saudon) se mana farmaya, Quteba ki riwayat mein ""aur agar kheti ho ke bajaey"" ya kheti ho ke alfaz hain."
3900,"Younus, Suhak aur Musa-bin-Aqba sab ne Naafe se isi sanad ke sath un (Ubaidullah, Ayub aur Leis) ki hadis ki tarah hadis bayan ki."
3901,"Yahya-bin-Yahya ne kaha : maine Imam Malik ke samney qirat ki, unhon-ne Naafe se aur unhon-ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jisne khajoor ka aisa darakht farokht kya jis par nar khajoor ka bor daala gaya ho to uska phal farokht karne waley ka hai siwaey-iske ke khareedaar ( Sauda ke doran mein) shart tay kar ley."
3902,"Ubaidullah ne hamein Naafe se hadis bayan ki aur unhon-ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : khajoor ka jo darakht khareeda gaya aur uski taabeer ki gaee thi to uska phal usi ke liye hai jisne taabeer ki, magar ye ke wo aadmi jisne usey khareeda ( saudey mein uski ( shart tay kar ley."
3903,"Leis ne hamein Naafe se, unhon-ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jisne khajoor ki taabeer ( nar khajoor ka bor daal kar uski pardakht) ki phir iske darakht ko bech diya, to khajoor ka phal usi ka hai jisne taabeer ki, siwaey-iske ke kharidney wala shart tay kar ley."
3904,Ayub ne Naafe se isi sanad ke sath isi tarah riwayat ki.
3905,"Leis ne hamein ibne-Shahab se khabar di, unhon-ne Salim bin-Abdullah-bin umr se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna aap farma rahe they : jisne taabeer kiye janey ke baad khajoor ka darakht khareeda, to uska phal usi ka hai jisne usey becha, siwaey-iske ke khareedaar shart tay kar ley aur jisne ghulam khareedaa to uska maal usi ka hai jisne usey farokht kya, siwaey-iske ke khareedaar shart tay kar ley."
3906,Sufiyan-bin-Uena ne Zohri se isi sanad ke sath usi ki tarah riwayat ki.
3907,"Yunus ne mujhey ibne-Shahab se khabar di, kaha : mujhey Salim bin-Abdullah-bin umr ne hadis bayan ki ke unke walid ne kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, aap farma rahe they. usi ki tarah ."
3908,"Sufiyan-bin-Uena ne hamein ibne-Juraij se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Ata se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Muhaaqla , Muzaabna , mukhaahira aur) pakney ki) salahiyatein zahir honey se pahley phalon ke saudey se mana farmaya aur) hukm diya ke) araayaa (ki Sauda (ke siwa ( phal ya kheti ko) sirf Dinar aur dirham ke iwaz hi farokht kiya jaey."
3909,"abu-Aasim ne hamein khabar di, kaha : hamein ibne-Juraij ne ata aur abu-Zubair se khabar di, un donon ne Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, wo keh rahe they : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mana farmaya, padhi. aagey usi ki tarah bayan kiya."
3910,"mukhlid-bin-Yazeed-jazri ne hamein khabar di, kaha : hamein ibne-Juraij ne hadis sunai, unhon-ne kaha : mujhey Ata ne Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se khabar di ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mukhaahira , Muhaaqla , Muzaabna aur khaney ke qaabil honey se pahley phalon ki farokht karne se mana farmaya. aur (hukm diya ke phalon aur ajnaas ki) sirf dirham aur Dinar hi se Sauda kiya jaey, siwaey araayaa ke. Ata ne kaha : Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) ne un alfaz ki wazaahat (viyakhiya) kartey huey kaha : mukhaahira se murad wo chatiyal zamin hai jo aik aadmi doosrey ke hawale karey to wo usmein kharch karey, phir wo ( zamin dene wala ( uski paidawar mein se hissey ley. aur unka khayal hai ke Muzaabna se murad khajoor par lagi hui taaza khajoor ki khushk khajoor (ki mutaiyna miqdar (ke iwaz Sauda hai aur Muhaaqla ye hai ke aadmi khadi fasl ko maaptey huey ghalley ke iwaz baich de."
3911,"Zaid-bin-abi-Unaisaa se riwayat hai, unhon-ne kaha : ham se abu-Waleed Makki ne hadis bayan ki jabke wo Ata-bin-abi-Ribah ke paas baithey huey they, unhon ( Zaid ( ne Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Muhaaqla , Muzaabna , mukhaahira aur is baat se mana farmaya hai ke ishqaah se pahley ( darakht par laga hua) khajoor (ka phal ( khareedaa jaey. ishqaah ye hai ke usmein surkhi ya zardi paida ho jaey ya usmein se kuchh khaya ja sakey ( Sara phal eik hi waqt nahi biktaa , kuchh khaney ke qaabil ho jaey to Sauda jaaiz hai.) aur Muhaaqla ye hai ke kheti ke saudey ghalley ki mutaiyan miqdar ( saa , wasq wghaira ya wazan (ke sath ki jaey aur Muzaabna ye hai ke darakht par lagi khajoor ke saudey khushk khajoor ki) maap ya tol ke zariey se) mutaiyan miqdar ke sath ki jaey aur mukhaahira ye hai ke zamin ko) jawaz ki shart poori kiye baghair ( tehai , chothai ya is tarah ke) kisi mutaiyan ( hissey ke iwaz ( batai par) diya jaey. Zaid ne kaha : maine ( sath baithey ( Ata-bin-abi-Ribah (Rehmatullahi-alaih) se puchha : kya aap ne ( bhi) Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ko Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se ye hadis bayan kartey huey sunaa? unhon-ne jawab diya : haan."
3912,"Sulaim-bin-hayyaan ne hamein hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein Saeed-bin-Mina ne Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Muzaabna , Muhaaqla , mukhaahira aur rang tabdeel honey ( ishqaah ( se pahley phalon ke saudey se mana farmaya, (Sulaim-bin-hayyaan ne) kaha : maine Saeed se puchha : ishqaah se kya murad hai? unhon-ne kaha : unmein surkhi aur zardi paida ho jaey aur is mein se khaya ja sakey."
3913,"Hammad-bin-Zaid ne hamein hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein Ayub ne abu-Zubair aur Saeed-bin-Mina se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Muhaaqla , Muzaabna , muaawma , mukhaahira . padhi. un donon ( abu-Zubair aur Saeed ( mein se aik ne kaha : kai saalon ke liye Sauda karna hi muaawma hai. aur istisnaa wali saudey se mana farmaya aur araayaa (ko khushk phal ke iwaz bechney ( ki ijazat di."
3914,"Ismail bin-Ulaih ne hamein Ayub se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne abu-Zubair se, unhon-ne Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki. padhi. usi ki tarah , albatta unhon-ne ye zikr nahi kiya ke kai saalon ke liye Sauda karna hi muaawma hai."
3915,"ribaah-bin-abi Maruf ne hamein hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine Ata se suna, unhon-ne Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne zamin ko) uski apni paidawar ke badley kiraaey par deyne, us (ke phal ( ko kai saalon ke liye bechney aur pakney se pahley phalon ke saudey se mana farmaya."
3916,"Hammad-bin-Zaid ne hamein Matar warraaq se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Ata se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne zamin ko kiraaey par deney se mana farmaya."
3917,"Mehdi-bin-Memnon ne hamein hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein Matar warraaq ne Ata se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jis shakhs ki zamin ho to ( behtar hai) wo usey khud kaasht kare. agar wo khud kaasht na karey to apne bhai ko kaasht kaari ke liye de dey."
3918,"Auzai ne Ata se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke kuchh sahaba ke paas zarurat se zayed zameenein thin to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jiske paas zarurat se zayed zamin ho wo ya to usey khud kaasht karey ya apne bhai ko udhaar de dey . agar wo nahi maanta to wo apni zamin apne paas rakh ley. (kisi ghair sharaee tareeqey se kiraaey par na de.)"
3919,"Bukair-bin-Akhnas ne Ata se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mana farmaya ke zamin ki ujrat ( kiraaya (ya ( uski honey wali paidawar ka ( mutaiyan ( miqdar mein) hissey liya jaey."
3920,"Abdul-Malik ne hamein Ata se hadis bayan ki aur unhon-ne Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jiske paas zamin ho, wo usey khud kaasht karey, agar wo usmein kaashtkaari ki istitaat na paaey aur aajiz ho to ( behtar hai) apne kisi musalman bhai ko aariyatan (udhaar) de dey aur uske sath zamin ki ujrat ka mamla na kare."
3921,"Hammam ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : Sulaiman-bin-Musa ne Ata se sawal kiya aur kaha : kya aapko Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ne hadis bayan ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jiske paas zamin ho (to behtar hai) wo usey kaasht karey ya apne bhai ko kaashtkaari ke liye de dey aur usey kiraaey par na de? unhon-ne jawab diya : haan."
3922,Amr (bin-Dinar) ne Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mukhaahira (ghalat sharton ke sath batai par diye) se mana farmaya.
3923,"Saeed-bin-Mina ne hamein hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, wo keh rahe they ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jiske paas faaltu zamin ho wo usey khud kaasht karey ya apne bhai ko kaashtkaari ke liye de dey aur usey (istifaadey (fayda uthaney) ke liye) farokht na karo. main (Sulaim-bin-hayyaan) ne Saeed se puchha : usey farokht na karo se kya murad hai? kya aap ki murad kiraaye par deney se thi? unhon-ne jawab diya : haan."
3924,"Zuhair ne hamein hadis bayan ki, kaha : abu-Zubair ne hamein Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke zamaney mein zamin batai par detey aur) baqi saari paidawar mein se hissey ke ilawa ( gahey janey ke baad khoshon mein bach janey wali gandam aur is tarah ki cheezein (pani ki guzargaahon ke ird-gird honey wali paidawar ( wasool kartey to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jiske paas zamin ho wo usey khud kaasht karey ya apne kisi bhai ko kaasht kaari ke liye  (aariyatan (udhaar)) de dey warna usey ( khali ( padaa rehney de."
3925,"Hisham-bin-Sad ne mujhey hadis bayan ki ke unhein abu-Zubair Makki ne hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, wo keh rahe they : ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke zamaney mein tehai ya chothai hissey ke iwaz , naalon (ke kinaron ki paidawar (ke iwaz zamin letey they. to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) us barey mein) khutba dene ke liye) khadey huey aur farmaya : jiske paas zamin ho to ( behtar hai) wo usey kaasht kare. agar wo khud usey kaasht nahi karta to apne bhai ko aariyatan (udhaar) de dey. agar wo usey apne bhai ko bhi nahi deta to usko apne paas rakh ley."
3926,"abu-Awana ne hamein Sulaiman (Aamash) se hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein Abu-Sufiyan ( Talha-bin-Naafe ( ne Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, aap farma rahe they : jiske paas zamin ho to ( behtar hai ke) wo usey hiba (hadiya) karey ya aariyatan (udhaar) de dey."
3927,"Ammar-bin-ruzzaiq ne Aamash se isi sanad ke sath yahi hadis bayan ki, albatta unhon-ne kaha : wo usey kaasht karey ya kisi aur aadmi ko kaasht kaari ke liye de dey."
3928,"Bukair ne hadis bayan ki ke unhein Abdullah-bin-Ubai Salma ne Nauman-bin-abi-Ayash se hadis bayan ki aur unhon-ne Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne zamin ko (mamnooa' (mana kiye hue) tareeqey se) kiraaey par deney se mana farmaya. Bukair ne kaha : mujhey Naafe ne hadis bayan ki ke unhon-ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, wo keh rahe they : ham apni zameenein batai par detey they. phir jab ham ne Hazrat Rafe-bin-Khadeej (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadis suni to usey tark kar diya."
3929,"abu-Zubair ne Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne khali zamin ki do ya teen saalon ke liye Sauda karne se mana farmaya."
3930,"Saeed-bin-Mansoor , abu-Bakar-bin-abi-Sheba , Amr Naqid aur Zuhair-bin-Harab ne kaha : hamein Sufiyan-bin-Uena ne Humaid Aaraj se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Sulaiman-bin-ateeq se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kai saalon ke saudey se mana farmaya. abu-Bakar-bin-abi-Sheba ki riwayat mein hai : phalon ke kai saal ke liye saudey se ( mana farmaya )."
3931,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jiski zamin ho wo usey khud kaasht karey ya apne bhai ko aariyatan (udhaar) de dey , agar wo nahi maantaa to apni zamin apne paas rakhey. ( ghalat tareeqey se batai par na de. ("
3932,"Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ne khabar di ke unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, aap Muzaabna aur huqool se mana farma rahe they. Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : Muzaabna se murad ( khajoor par lagey ( phal ki khushk khajoor se Sauda hai aur haqool se murad zamin ko) uski paidawar ke mutaiyan hissey ke iwaz ( batai par dena hai."
3933,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Muhaaqla aur Muzaabna se mana farmaya."
3934,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Muzaabna aur Muhaaqla se mana farmaya, Muzaabna darakht par lagi khajoor ko) khushk khajoor ke iwaz ( khareednaa hai aur Muhaaqla se murad zamin ko kiraaey par dena hai."
3935,"Hammad-bin-Zaid ne hamein Amr (bin-Dinar ( se khabar di, unhon-ne kaha : maine Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, wo keh rahe they : ham mukhaabira mein koi harj nahi samajhtey they yahan tak ke wo pahlaa saal aaya jis mein) Yazeed ki imaarat ke liye bait li gai) to Hazrat Raafe (Raziallahu anhu) ne khayal kiya ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us se mana farmaya hai."
3936,"Sufiyan (bin-Uena ), Ayub aur Sufiyan ( Sory ( sab ne Amr-bin-Dinar se isi sanad ke sath usi ki tarah riwayat ki aur ibne-Uena ki hadis mein ye izafa kiya : to ham ne un ( Raafe (Raziallahu anhu)) ki wjah se ( ehtiyaatan ( usey chhod diya."
3937,"Mujahid se riwayat hai, unhon-ne kaha : Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : Raafe (Raziallahu anhu) ne hamari zamin ka fayda ham se rok diya."
3938,"Yazeed-bin-Zaree ne hamein Ayub se khabar di aur unhon-ne Naafe se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke ahad mein aur Hazrat Abu-Bakar , umr aur Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ke doure-imaarat mein aur Hazrat Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) ki khilafat ke shuruati dinon tak Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) apni zaminon ko batai par detey they yahan tak ke Hazrat Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) ki khilafat ke aakhiri dinon mein unhein ye baat pahunchi ke Hazrat Rafe-bin-Khadeej (Raziallahu anhu) iske barey mein Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se manaahi bayan kartey hain, chunanche wo unke paas gaey, mein bhi unke sath tha, unhon-ne unse malum kiya to unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) zaminon ko batai par deney se mana farmatey they. iske baad ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne usey chhod diya. iskey baad jab Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se iske barey mein puchha jata to wo kehtey : Rafe-bin-Khadeej (Raziallahu anhu) ka khayal hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us se mana farmaya hai."
3939,"Hammad-bin-Zaid aur Ismail ( ibne-Ulaih ( donon ne Ayub se isi sanad ke sath usi ki tarah hadis bayan ki aur ibne-Ulaih ki hadis mein ye izafa hai, kaha : iske baad Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne usey chhod diya aur wo usey (apni zamin ko) kiraaey par nahi detey they."
3940,"Ubaidullah ne hamein Naafe se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : main Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath Hazrat Rafe-bin-Khadeej (Raziallahu anhu) ki taraf gaya yahan tak wo unke paas balaat ke maqam par pahunchey to unhon-ne unhein ( ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ko) bataya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne zaminon ko kiraaey par deney se mana farmaya tha."
3941,Hakam ne Naafe se aur unhon-ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke wo Hazrat Raafe (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas aaey. padhi. phir (unke hawale se) yahi hadis Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat kartey huey bayan ki.
3942,"Husain-bin-Hasan-bin-Yasar ne hamein hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein Ibne-Aun ne Naafe se hadis bayan ki ke Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) zamin ko ujrat par detey they, kaha : unhein Hazrat Rafe-bin-Khadeej (Raziallahu anhu) ke hawale se hadis batai gaee, kaha : wo mere sath unke yahaan gaey to unhon-ne apne kuchh chachaon se bayan kiya. unhon-ne is hadis mein Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se bayan kiya ke aap ne zamin ko kiraaey par deney se mana farmaya hai. kaha : to Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne usey chhod diya aur zamin ujrat par na di."
3943,Yazid-bin-Harun ne kaha : hamein Ibne-Aun ne isi sanad ke sath hadis bayan ki aur kaha : unhon-ne apne kuchh chachaon ke waastey se Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se ye hadis bayan ki.
3944,Saalim-bin-Abdullah ne khabar di ke Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) apni zameenein kiraaey par detey they yahan tak ke unhein ye baat pahunchi ke Hazrat Rafe-bin-Khadeej (Raziallahu anhu) zamin ko kiraaey par deney se mana kartey hain. chunanche Hazrat Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ne unse mulaqat ki aur kaha : ibne-khadeej ! aap zamin ko kiraaey par dene ke barey mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se kya bayan kartey hain? Hazrat Rafe-bin-Khadeej (Raziallahu anhu) ne Hazrat Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se kaha : maine apne do chachaon se suna aur wo donon badr mein Sharik huey they. wo apne gharaaney ke logon ko hadis bayan kar rahe they ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne zamin ko batai par deney se mana farmaya hai. Hazrat Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke zamaney mein ba-khoobi janta tha ke zamin kiraaey par di jati thi. phir Hazrat Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ko khof hua ke (mumkin hai) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne iske barey mein koi nayaa hukm jari kiya ho jiska unhein ilm na hua ho. lihaza unhon-ne zamin ko kiraaey par dena chhod diya.
3945,"Ismail-bin-Ulaih ne hamein Ayub se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Yala-bin-Hakim se, unhon-ne Sulaiman-bin-Yasar se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Rafe-bin-Khadeej (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke zamaney mein ham zamin ko uski paidawar ke hissey par detey they aur usey tehai aur chothai hissey aur (iske saath) mutaiyan miqdar mein ghalley ke iwaz kiraaey par detey. aik roz hamarey paas mere chachaon mein se aik aadmi aaya aur kehney laga : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hamein aik aisey kaam se mana kiya hai jo hamarey liye nafa mand tha lekin Allah aur uske rasool ki itaat hamarey liye zyada nafa bakhsh hai. aap ne hamein mana kiya hai ke ham zamin ko batai par dein aur usey tehai aur chothai hissey aur mutaiyan ghalley ke iwaz kiraaey par dein. aur aap ne zamin ke Malik ko hukm diya ke wo khud usmein kaasht karey ya kaasht ke liye (apne musalman bhai ko) de dey aur aap ne iske kiraaey par deine aur uske siwa ( ghalley ke aik mutaiyan hissey par deine) ko na-pasand kiya hai."
3946,"Hammad-bin-Zaid ne hamein Ayub se khabar di, unhon-ne kaha : Yala-bin-Hakim ne meri taraf likha , unhon-ne kaha : maine Sulaiman-bin-Yasar se suna, wo Hazrat Rafe-bin-Khadeej (Raziallahu anhu) se hadis bayan kar rahe they. unhon-ne kaha : ham zamin ko batai par detey aur usey tehai aur chothai hissey par kiraaey par detey they. aagey ibne-Ulaih ki (pichhli ( hadis ki tarah bayan kiya."
3947,ibne-abi-Aruba ne Yala-bin-Hakim se isi sanad ke sath usi ki tarah riwayat bayan ki.
3948,"Jareer-bin-Haazim ne Yala-bin-Hakim ki isi sanad ke sath riwayat ki, unhon-ne ( Sulaiman ke waastey se) Rafe-bin-Khadeej (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne (apne chachaon mein se aik (ke alfaz nahi kahey."
3949,"abu-Amr Auzai ne mujhey Rafe-bin-Khadeej (Raziallahu anhu) ke aazad karda ghulam abu-Najaashi se hadis bayan ki aur unhon-ne Hazrat Raafe (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki Zuhair-bin-Raafe unke chacha they, kaha : Zuher (Raziallahu anhu) mere paas aaey to unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik aisey kaam se mana farmaya hai jo hamein sahoolat dene wala tha. maine puchha : wo kya hai? Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne jo farmaya wo bar-haq hai. kaha : aap ne mujh se puchha : tum apne kheton ka kya mamla kartey ho? maine kaha : aey Allah ke rasool ! ham unhein chhoti nehar (ke kinaron ki paidawar ( par ya khajoor ya jau ke (mutaiyena) wasqon par ujrat par detey hain. aap ne farmaya : to aisa na karo, usey khud kaasht karo ya kaasht ke liye kisi ko de do ya waisey hi apne hath mein rakho."
3950,"Ikrima-bin-Ammar ne abu-Najaashi se, unhon-ne Hazrat Raafe (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se yahi hadis riwayat ki aur unhon-ne apne chacha Zuher (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ka tazkira nahi kiya."
3951,Imam Malik ne Rabee-bin-abi-Abdur-Rehman se aur unhon-ne Hanzala-bin-Qais se riwayat ki ke unhon-ne Hazrat Rafe-bin-Khadeej (Raziallahu anhu) se zamin ko kiraaey par dene ke barey mein malum kiya to unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne zamin ko kiraaey par deney se mana farmaya hai. kaha : maine puchha : kya soney aur chandi ke iwaz bhi ? unhon-ne jawab diya : albatta soney aur chandi ke iwaz dene mein koi harj nahi.
3952,"Auzai ne hamein Rabeea-bin-abi-Abdur-Rehman se hadis bayan ki, kaha : mujhey Hanzala-bin-Qais Ansari ne hadis sunai, unhon-ne kaha : maine Hazrat Rafe-bin-Khadeej (Raziallahu anhu) se soney aur chandi ( Dinar aur dirham (ke iwaz zamin ko batai par dene ke barey mein sawal kiya to unhon-ne kaha : usmein koi harj nahi. (baat hona ye hai ke) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke ahad mein log nehron ki zamin , chhotey naalon ke kinaron ki zamin aur) mutaiyan miqdar mein) fasl ki kuchh cheezon ke iwaz zamin ujrat par detey they. kabhi ye ( hissey ( tabah ho jata aur wo mehfooz rehta aur kabhi ye mehfooz rehta aur wo tabah ho jata. logon mein batai ( kiraaey par deine ( ki sirf yahi sura thi. isi liye us se mana kiya gaya. albatta malum aur mehfooz cheez jiski adaaeygi ki zamaanat di ja sakti ho to usmein koi harj nahi."
3953,"Sufiyan-bin-Uena ne hamein Yahya-bin-Saeed se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Hanzala zurqi se riwayat ki ke unhon-ne Hazrat Rafe-bin-Khadeej (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, wo keh rahe they : Ansar mein sabse zyada hamarey khet they. kaha : ham zamin ko is shart par kiraaey par detey ke ye ( hissey ( hamarey liye hai aur wo ( hissey ( unke liye hai. kabhi-kabhi is hissey mein paidawar hoti aur is mein na hoti, to aap ne hamein is se mana kar diya. albatta aap ne hamein chandi ke iwaz deney se mana nahi kiya."
3954,Hammad aur Yazid-bin-Harun ne Yahya-bin-Saeed se isi sanad ke sath usi ke ham-mana hadis bayan ki.
3955,"Yahya-bin-Yahya ne kaha : hamein abdul-Wahid bin Ziyad ne khabar di, neez abu-Bakar-bin-abi-Sheba ne kaha : hamein Ali-bin-Mus-hir ne hadis bayan ki, un donon ( abdul-Wahid aur Ali ( ne ( Sulaiman ( Shebani se aur unhon-ne Abdullah-bin Saaib se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine Abdullah-bin Maaqil se muzaar'at ( zamin ki paidawar ki mutaiyan miqdar par batai (ke barey mein puchha to unhon-ne kaha : mujhey Hazrat Sabit bin Suhak (Raziallahu anhu) ne khabar di ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne muzaar'at se mana farmaya, ibne-Abi-Sheba ki riwayat mein hai : aap ne us se mana farmaya aur unhon-ne kaha : maine ibne- Maaqil se poochha. Abdullah ka naam nahi liya."
3956,"abu-Awana ne hamein Sulaiman Shebani se khabar di, unhon-ne Abdullah-bin Saaib se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : ham Abdullah-bin Maaqil ke paas gaey, ham ne unse muzaar'at ke barey mein sawal kya to unhon-ne kaha : Hazrat Sabit (Raziallahu anhu) ka khayal hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne muzaar'at se mana farmaya aur naqdi ke iwaz kiraaey par dene ka hukm diya hai aur farmaya : usmein koi harj nahi."
3957,"Hammad-bin-Zaid ne hamein Amr (bin Dinar ( se khabar di ke Mujahid ne Taaus se kaha : hamarey sath Hazrat Rafe-bin-Khadeej (Raziallahu anhu) ke betey ke paas chalo aur unse unke walid ke waastey se Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki hui hadis suno, kaha : unhon (Taaus ( ne unhein daanta aur kaha : Allah ki qism : agar mujhey ilm hota ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us se mana farmaya hai to main ye kaam (kabhi) na karta lekin mujhey us shakhs ne hadis bayan ki jo usey un sabse zyada jaanney wala hai, unki murad Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se thi ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : tum mein se koi apni zamin apne bhai ko aariyatan de, ye uske liye us se behtar hai ke is par mutaiyan paidawar wsool kare. (is se Allah ki raza bhi hasil hogi aur jhagdon se mehfooz bhi rahega. ("
3958,"Sufiyan ne hamein Amr aur ibne-Taaus se hadis bayan ki aur unhon-ne Taaus se riwayat ki ke wo (naqdi ke iwaz) batai par zamin detey they. Amr ne kaha : maine unse kaha : abu Abdur-Rehman ! agar aap mukhaahira chhod dein (to behtar hai) kyonke log samajhtey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mukhaahira se mana farmaya hai. unhon-ne kaha : Amr ! mujhey is masley ko un sab ki nisbat zyada jaanney waale, yani Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne bataya hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us se mana nahi farmaya, aap ne to sirf farmaya tha : tum mein se koi apne bhai ko) zamin ( aariyatan de ye uske liye uski nisbat behtar hai ke is par mutaiyan paidawar wsool kare. (bila iwaz deney se usey ghair mutaiyan, wasee nafa hasil hoga)"
3959,"Ayub, Sufiyan, ibne-Juraij aur Shoba sab ne Amr-bin-Dinar se, unhon-ne Taaus se, unhon-ne Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se unki hadis ki tarah bayan kya."
3960,"Mamar ne ibne-Taaus se, unhon-ne apne walid se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : tum mein se koi apni zamin apne bhai ko de ye uske liye us se behtar hai ke is par itna itna, yani mutaiyan miqdar mein wsool kare. kaha : Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : yahi haql hai aur Ansar ki zaban mein Muhaaqla hai."
3961,"Abdul-Malik bin Zaid ne Taaus se, unhon-ne Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki, aap ne farmaya : jiski zamin ho, wo agar usey apne bhai ko aariyatan de dey to ye uske liye behtar hai."
